International Telephone andTelegraph Corp said its long distance unit lowered rates fortwo of its WATS services.    ITT said it lowered its SMART-WATS rate an average of 9.3pct, and its preferred WATS rates four pct.    In addition to the rate reduction, ITT said it also loweredits monthly preferred WATS service charge for each location to925 dlrs, a reduction of 75 dlrs. Reuter&#3;